I do not mind recalling that our first tryst was a flop. It took me solong to persuade her that this was the day, and she made such a fuss aboutwhich ultimate inch of clothing could be removed and which parts of her bodyVenus, the Virgin, and the maire of our arrondissement allowed to betouched, that by the time I had her in a passably convenient position ofsurrender, I was an impotent wreck. We were lying naked, in